title: Andrzej Slawinski - Water Planet Audiostrobe CD [FLAC]
description:
Audiostrobe CD for those of you with Audiostrobe compatible Mind Machines.

Andrzej Slawinski is the guiding force behind Tamas Laboratorium, a well known and critically acclaimed developer of psych-acoustic music in Europe. This collection comprises some of the best from the European releases. In addition to audio remixing, each selection has been enhanced with a dynamic light experience to create an exciting and entertaining psycho-acoustic light/sound event.
